        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><ol><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;"><strong>Day 1- 20:</strong> Learn React theories</li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;"><strong>Day 20–60:</strong> Built 4 React and MERN projects</li></ol></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
